OL,4,CMary Beard's 'retirement present' to
OL,5,Cfund students
OL,6, Historian Mary Beard is to fund
OL,7, scholarships for two disadvantaged
OL,8, students to study classics at Cambridge
OL,9, University, as a "retirement present".
OL,11,FThe Cambridge professor is stepping
OL,12,Fdown next year after almost 40 years of
OL,13,Fteaching and research.
OL,15,FShe described the #80,000 donation as
OL,16,Fher "payback time".
OL,18,F"I am very conscious of what I've
OL,19,Fgained from classics, no-one from my
OL,20,Ffamily had a university degree," said
OL,21,FDame Mary.
